WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:08.000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:08.000 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 33]

01:29.240 --> 01:30.250
Uncle, save me!

01:32.470 --> 01:32.890
Let's go.

01:34.160 --> 01:34.650
Out of the way!

01:40.440 --> 01:40.980
Uncle.

01:41.270 --> 01:42.220
Miaoqing is hurt!

02:33.390 --> 02:34.300
The child is gone.

02:35.270 --> 02:35.970
Get some rest.

02:52.040 --> 02:52.650
Take a sip.

03:05.990 --> 03:06.530
Drink it.

03:19.590 --> 03:20.810
I hate you.

03:23.240 --> 03:24.570
I hate you.

03:55.150 --> 03:56.500
I hate you!

04:33.030 --> 04:34.060
Immortal Lord Xuanhua,

04:35.080 --> 04:36.420
why such a grand display?

04:37.270 --> 04:38.500
What brings you here?

04:51.470 --> 04:52.300
Mr. Zuo Qiu,

04:53.390 --> 04:55.420
I respect the academy as a pillar of the immortal sects,

04:56.080 --> 04:56.940
always staying out of conflict.

04:57.680 --> 04:59.620
But now you're harboring the Demon Lord and the Divine Tree.

05:00.230 --> 05:01.100
What are you trying to do?

05:02.080 --> 05:03.570
Are you betraying the immortal sects

05:04.390 --> 05:05.370
to side with those across the sea?

05:06.080 --> 05:09.250
The academy has only masters and disciples.

05:09.960 --> 05:11.740
No Demon Lord or Divine Tree.

05:13.520 --> 05:15.500
A few days ago, an assassin came after me,

05:16.760 --> 05:18.890
but was rescued by the Demon Lord Yecha and the Divine Tree.

05:19.270 --> 05:21.250
That assassin was struck by my fire lotus spell.

05:21.830 --> 05:23.210
With a little push...

05:40.230 --> 05:40.770
Look.

05:41.760 --> 05:43.810
The assassin, Baili Gelin, is at the academy.

05:44.910 --> 05:47.620
The Divine Tree and the Demon Lord are here too.

05:49.830 --> 05:50.570
Ji Tongzhou,

05:52.030 --> 05:53.570
you killed Changyue and Ye!

05:54.270 --> 05:55.660
As long as I draw breath,

05:56.230 --> 05:57.540
I will kill you for revenge!

05:58.270 --> 05:58.810
Don't move.

05:58.830 --> 06:00.060
I'll say it once more.

06:00.590 --> 06:02.890
The academy has only masters and disciples.

06:03.590 --> 06:05.130
No Demon Lord, Divine Tree,

06:05.830 --> 06:06.890
or assassin.

06:07.270 --> 06:08.940
Since you insist,

06:09.710 --> 06:11.370
don't blame me for being rude.

06:12.000 --> 06:12.500
Search.

06:12.520 --> 06:13.130
Yes.

06:13.320 --> 06:13.940
Don't you dare!

06:23.790 --> 06:24.620
Immortal Lord Xuanhua,

06:25.270 --> 06:26.940
Chufeng Academy is a sacred ground of the immortal sects.

06:27.270 --> 06:29.060
They've always stayed out of disputes.

06:29.880 --> 06:32.420
You brazenly disrupt the peace of the academy.

06:32.910 --> 06:34.210
Aren't you afraid of public outrage?

06:45.790 --> 06:46.420
Fine.

06:47.880 --> 06:49.690
Out of respect for the academy's teachings,

06:51.000 --> 06:52.330
I'll give you one day.

06:53.120 --> 06:54.890
Hand over the Demon Lord and the Divine Tree by tomorrow morning.

06:55.470 --> 06:56.100
Otherwise,

06:57.680 --> 06:59.370
I'll burn Chufeng Academy to the ground

07:03.910 --> 07:05.180
and smoke them out.

07:48.590 --> 07:49.890
I knew you two were still alive.

07:51.030 --> 07:52.300
All these years, every divination I made

07:52.590 --> 07:54.130
pointed to a reunion with old friends.

07:56.680 --> 07:57.620
Do you two

07:57.960 --> 07:58.690
have any conscience at all?

07:59.200 --> 07:59.890
You're fine,

07:59.910 --> 08:01.890
and you didn't even send word?

08:02.120 --> 08:02.890
Deng,

08:04.150 --> 08:05.690
you're a Sect Leader now.

08:05.910 --> 08:07.300
Can you at least act like one?

08:10.080 --> 08:10.740
You left

08:11.880 --> 08:13.130
for ten whole years.

08:13.760 --> 08:15.450
Do you know how worried your master was?

08:16.390 --> 08:17.420
How is

08:18.080 --> 08:18.810
my master?

08:20.710 --> 08:22.690
His cultivation has dropped sharply.

08:23.270 --> 08:24.940
He's retired to Hushe Peak now.

08:27.390 --> 08:29.250
But he's quite carefree these days.

08:29.910 --> 08:31.210
He often discusses medicine and the Dao

08:31.230 --> 08:32.980
with Elder Dongyang and Elder Zhu.

08:35.560 --> 08:36.940
I almost forgot the main thing.

08:40.440 --> 08:41.420
Elder Dongyang asked me

08:41.440 --> 08:42.780
to bring you this miraculous pill.

08:43.400 --> 08:44.780
He said your cultivation has declined.

08:44.920 --> 08:45.730
Take this,

08:45.870 --> 08:47.060
and it'll secure your future well-being.

08:48.710 --> 08:50.210
They're always so thoughtful.

08:50.800 --> 08:52.490
Xiuyuan and I could really use some medicine right now.

08:55.350 --> 08:56.300
Only one pill?

08:58.750 --> 08:59.450
What do you mean?

09:00.280 --> 09:02.180
Your master traveled far and wide,

09:02.200 --> 09:02.970
searching for the finest herbs,

09:02.990 --> 09:03.970
just to refine this single pill.

09:09.800 --> 09:10.540
You've just been hurt.

09:11.280 --> 09:11.850
Take it.

09:28.200 --> 09:28.940
I still have my spirit root.

09:29.230 --> 09:29.780
I can recultivate.

09:29.960 --> 09:30.420
You...

09:39.510 --> 09:40.570
My spirit power is back?

09:43.510 --> 09:45.420
The pill only strengthens the body and prolongs life.

09:45.960 --> 09:49.060
Your spirit power must have returned because of the medicine.

09:49.470 --> 09:50.180
It only works once.

09:52.750 --> 09:54.490
It doesn't matter. It's still a gain.

09:56.680 --> 09:57.090
By the way,

09:57.630 --> 09:59.490
Ji Tongzhou gave the academy a one-day ultimatum.

10:00.470 --> 10:01.140
What do you two think?

10:07.960 --> 10:09.180
Fight him to the death!

10:14.750 --> 10:15.300
Gelin,

10:15.870 --> 10:17.090
you were imprisoned and wounded.

10:17.110 --> 10:17.900
Your spirit power is weak.

10:18.280 --> 10:19.140
You should return to the East Sea.

10:19.830 --> 10:20.940
No, I don't want to run away.

10:22.630 --> 10:24.060
If I don't avenge Changyue and Ye,

10:24.510 --> 10:25.850
I'll never have peace.

10:27.470 --> 10:28.380
Even if it costs me my life,

10:29.470 --> 10:30.660
I'll fight him to the end.

10:32.080 --> 10:34.020
Ji Tongzhou has been crushing his opponents for these years.

10:34.830 --> 10:35.940
He's made plenty of enemies.

10:36.870 --> 10:39.090
Lately, Xingzheng Hall has wiped out several immortal sects.

10:39.560 --> 10:41.260
Wuyue Court also wants to curb his ambitions.

10:41.680 --> 10:42.570
This is our chance.

10:43.680 --> 10:45.090
But what exactly is

10:45.470 --> 10:46.490
the karmic fire?

10:47.280 --> 10:49.060
Karmic fire comes from the inner demon.

10:50.160 --> 10:51.730
Mr. Zuo Qiu found the Xuanhua Sacred Fire Record

10:51.750 --> 10:52.780
in Futu Tower.

10:53.350 --> 10:54.060
It says

10:54.470 --> 10:55.380
those who wield karmic fire

10:55.800 --> 10:57.060
are usually people with deep obsessions,

10:57.470 --> 10:58.450
driven to the brink of despair.

10:58.800 --> 10:59.260
The fire

10:59.350 --> 11:01.090
is their only weapon of retaliation.

11:01.590 --> 11:03.690
That's why it's also called the fire of the inner demon.

11:06.400 --> 11:07.450
Inner demon?

11:08.800 --> 11:09.660
Inner demon?

11:11.110 --> 11:13.260
Is this the aftermath of the mirage dream

11:13.630 --> 11:14.570
on Fanghu Island?

11:17.200 --> 11:18.730
Karmic fire is born from the inner demon.

11:19.710 --> 11:21.330
So if we get rid of the inner demon,

11:21.960 --> 11:23.690
the fire will die out?

11:24.830 --> 11:25.780
Not that easy.

11:26.230 --> 11:27.380
To get rid of the inner demon,

11:27.830 --> 11:29.140
you must first understand the obsession.

11:32.560 --> 11:33.610
I know what his obsession is.

11:35.040 --> 11:36.210
But even knowing it,

11:36.560 --> 11:38.810
we'd have to push him to the edge before we could act.

11:39.470 --> 11:40.490
And who in this world

11:41.110 --> 11:43.090
can push Immortal Lord Xuanhua to the edge?

11:50.830 --> 11:51.490
Let me try.

11:53.990 --> 11:55.330
Mr. Zuo already knew you'd say that.

11:56.200 --> 11:56.690
Follow me.

12:03.630 --> 12:04.900
Human strength has its limits.

12:05.470 --> 12:06.380
In just one day,

12:06.630 --> 12:08.810
how can Xiuyuan stand against Immortal Lord Xuanhua?

12:12.400 --> 12:13.690
One person's strength is limited.

12:15.230 --> 12:17.850
But when generations share the same will,

12:18.510 --> 12:20.090
spanning centuries without end,

12:21.160 --> 12:22.660
it becomes limitless.

12:24.680 --> 12:25.300
Sir.

12:44.560 --> 12:45.940
You only have one chance.

12:46.510 --> 12:47.690
Hold Ji Tongzhou back.

12:48.280 --> 12:50.210
Help Lifei turn the tide!

13:07.320 --> 13:08.940
Mr. Zuo, you gave him the academy's spirit energy.

13:10.040 --> 13:10.850
Thousands of years ago,

13:11.510 --> 13:12.940
I founded Chufeng Academy.

13:13.350 --> 13:16.780
It was meant to be a place beyond the affairs of this world.

13:17.510 --> 13:19.450
Yet all things in this world are connected.

13:20.110 --> 13:21.660
Nothing is truly detached.

13:22.320 --> 13:25.490
My spirit root was destroyed long ago.

13:25.960 --> 13:28.380
I've only survived on the academy's spirit energy.

13:28.750 --> 13:29.330
Now

13:29.710 --> 13:31.210
it's up to the younger generation.

13:31.920 --> 13:33.810
Mr. Zuo, you sacrificed your cultivation

13:34.230 --> 13:35.330
to build the mountain-sea barrier,

13:35.800 --> 13:36.900
protecting the Central Plains

13:37.630 --> 13:38.940
and preserving the flame of the immortal sects.

13:39.590 --> 13:44.020
From now on, it's these flames that will carry on.

13:52.510 --> 13:52.780
Mr...

13:55.870 --> 13:56.420
Mr. Zuo.

14:01.830 --> 14:03.570
With growth comes decay.

14:05.320 --> 14:06.610
Let nature take its course.

14:08.560 --> 14:09.780
Don't dwell on it.

14:48.230 --> 14:50.090
We don't know if we'll survive tomorrow's battle.

14:53.280 --> 14:55.780
I'm dragging you into this again.

14:57.350 --> 14:58.020
Silly.

14:59.230 --> 15:00.140
We're husband and wife.

15:00.990 --> 15:02.140
We live and die together.

15:18.590 --> 15:19.570
I want to stay at the academy.

15:21.040 --> 15:21.540
Why?

15:24.870 --> 15:27.690
When I was young, I relied on Changyue and Ye.

15:28.990 --> 15:29.850
In the East Sea,

15:30.750 --> 15:32.260
I had Jiao and you.

15:33.990 --> 15:36.090
I always hesitated before doing anything.

15:36.870 --> 15:38.020
My cultivation was average.

15:38.710 --> 15:39.420
I never knew

15:39.440 --> 15:40.900
what I truly wanted.

15:41.750 --> 15:42.540
But today,

15:44.510 --> 15:45.210
watching the masters

15:45.230 --> 15:46.780
stand up to Ji Tongzhou,

15:47.470 --> 15:48.420
I finally understood.

15:49.590 --> 15:50.780
Even dust may fight the storm.

15:51.560 --> 15:53.420
We ordinary people have our own reason for being.

15:55.080 --> 15:56.060
So I want to stay.

15:57.440 --> 15:59.300
I want to show my future juniors

16:00.470 --> 16:01.810
what it means that all beings are equal,

16:03.160 --> 16:04.660
to fear no power,

16:05.230 --> 16:06.380
to hold a sense of justice,

16:07.590 --> 16:08.540
and to walk the Great Dao.

16:09.830 --> 16:10.210
Alright.

16:13.470 --> 16:14.210
Then we'll

16:14.960 --> 16:15.970
seek the Great Dao together.

17:11.360 --> 17:12.450
You're finally here.

17:17.880 --> 17:18.660
Come at me together.

17:19.710 --> 17:21.180
Save me the trouble.

18:04.790 --> 18:05.250
Form the formation!

18:16.160 --> 18:17.730
Demon-Subduing Formation?

18:19.840 --> 18:21.660
You dare use that against me?

18:22.680 --> 18:23.580
Ridiculous.

20:39.230 --> 20:41.380
Fire and metal unite. The karmic fire is merciless.

20:41.990 --> 20:42.900
Your own karmic fire.

20:43.470 --> 20:43.970
Take it back!

21:00.120 --> 21:01.100
This is the academy's spirit energy?

21:01.840 --> 21:02.620
You are the Demon Lord.

21:02.920 --> 21:03.940
Why are they helping you?

21:04.400 --> 21:05.140
Spirit power knows no divide.

21:06.030 --> 21:07.010
Good and evil dwell in the heart!

21:23.400 --> 21:23.970
Tongzhou,

21:24.680 --> 21:25.620
you're at your end.

21:26.470 --> 21:27.290
Time to turn back.

22:07.070 --> 22:07.660
Tongzhou.

22:10.440 --> 22:12.340
Tongzhou, why are you asleep?

22:17.550 --> 22:18.180
Lanya?

22:20.070 --> 22:22.490
What... what are you doing here?

22:27.960 --> 22:28.900
What's wrong, Tongzhou?

22:29.750 --> 22:30.690
Do you hate me?

22:30.990 --> 22:32.180
Not happy to see me?

22:34.470 --> 22:36.250
I.. I am happy.

23:02.440 --> 23:03.010
Tongzhou,

23:03.840 --> 23:04.490
what's wrong?

23:04.920 --> 23:06.050
Did you not sleep well last night?

23:06.920 --> 23:07.770
Ye Ye?

23:09.400 --> 23:10.620
Ye Ye, you're alive?

23:13.030 --> 23:15.100
What are you talking about?

23:24.030 --> 23:24.620
Your Highness,

23:25.200 --> 23:26.180
you're still half asleep?

23:36.440 --> 23:37.450
Tongzhou, Mr. Hu is here.

23:37.640 --> 23:38.100
Sit down.

23:41.030 --> 23:42.450
Class is about to start.

23:42.960 --> 23:43.900
Do you all

23:44.840 --> 23:46.050
want to be punished?

23:51.070 --> 23:51.900
Ji Tongzhou!

23:53.230 --> 23:53.900
Dazing off?

23:55.440 --> 23:56.380
Still sleepy?

23:57.920 --> 23:58.820
Were you dreaming?

24:01.310 --> 24:01.900
A dream?

24:04.960 --> 24:05.730
Just a dream.

24:17.840 --> 24:18.770
It really was just a dream.

24:34.400 --> 24:34.970
Lifei.

24:37.840 --> 24:38.380
Lifei.

24:39.070 --> 24:39.690
Xiuyuan!

25:11.120 --> 25:12.620
Lifei! Xiuyuan!

25:15.070 --> 25:15.490
Lifei.

25:16.230 --> 25:17.770
I just had the longest dream.

25:18.440 --> 25:19.010
What did you dream about?

25:19.160 --> 25:19.730
I dreamed...

25:21.920 --> 25:23.860
Forget it. Don't tell dreams in broad daylight.

25:24.470 --> 25:25.940
My brother brought lots of food.

25:26.120 --> 25:27.100
Everyone will love it.

25:27.920 --> 25:29.140
Xiuyuan, join us.

25:30.360 --> 25:30.860
Let's go.

25:49.230 --> 25:50.100
Need to knead it more.

25:50.510 --> 25:51.730
- Changyue. - Like this.

25:52.790 --> 25:53.900
I got it, Changyue.

25:54.120 --> 25:54.900
You're doing so well.

25:56.200 --> 25:57.100
Almost done. See?

25:57.550 --> 25:58.010
Tongzhou,

25:58.880 --> 25:59.770
come make mooncakes with us.

26:05.680 --> 26:06.180
Done.

26:06.400 --> 26:07.380
Drink till we drop!

26:07.920 --> 26:08.490
Drink till we drop.

26:09.640 --> 26:10.180
Here.

26:13.400 --> 26:14.420
Come on.

26:16.880 --> 26:18.490
Let's release this wish lantern together.

26:19.030 --> 26:19.530
Sure.

26:19.990 --> 26:22.010
But what should we write?

26:29.120 --> 26:30.100
"May we be together forever."

26:30.920 --> 26:31.900
"The same every year."

26:32.600 --> 26:33.660
"May we be together forever."

26:34.750 --> 26:35.820
"The same every year."

26:37.230 --> 26:37.770
Alright.

26:55.440 --> 26:56.960
[May we be together forever. The same every year.]

27:02.160 --> 27:04.340
If only time could stop right here.

27:05.440 --> 27:06.380
Right, Tongzhou?

27:31.550 --> 27:32.050
Don't go!

27:47.790 --> 27:48.900
Immortal Lord Xuanhua?

27:53.160 --> 27:53.530
That...

28:00.270 --> 28:01.140
That's me?

28:15.640 --> 28:16.180
Tongzhou.

28:17.550 --> 28:18.210
Time to wake up.

28:26.030 --> 28:28.210
Tongzhou, we never blamed you.

28:35.030 --> 28:35.730
Sorry.

28:40.360 --> 28:40.970
I'm sorry.

28:55.710 --> 28:56.940
Why don't you blame me?

29:00.030 --> 29:01.770
I did so many wrong things.

29:11.400 --> 29:12.820
Why don't you blame me?

29:47.510 --> 29:49.900
A dream. Just a dream.

29:50.680 --> 29:52.100
All of this was a dream!

30:17.750 --> 30:18.490
What's happening?

30:20.710 --> 30:21.530
His mind is broken.

30:22.550 --> 30:23.620
He can't use Xuanhua Fire anymore.

30:31.550 --> 30:33.180
Ji Tongzhou, pay with your life!

30:57.990 --> 30:58.420
No.

31:11.400 --> 31:11.970
Miaoqing.

31:12.920 --> 31:13.530
Miaoqing.

31:14.040 --> 31:17.310
♪The warmth within my arms♪

31:17.310 --> 31:17.940
Miaoqing!

31:18.110 --> 31:21.150
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

31:21.450 --> 31:24.850
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

31:25.210 --> 31:26.790
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

31:26.790 --> 31:27.290
Miaoqing.

31:28.850 --> 31:30.920
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

31:30.920 --> 31:31.620
Your Highness.

31:32.960 --> 31:33.730
Does it hurt?

31:33.730 --> 31:35.570
♪I can no longer tell you♪

31:35.970 --> 31:39.170
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

31:39.450 --> 31:42.490
♪Utter that line♪

31:42.850 --> 31:44.570
♪Knowing love and hate♪

31:44.890 --> 31:48.200
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

31:48.200 --> 31:49.050
Your Highness.

31:50.170 --> 31:51.770
♪I still linger on♪

31:52.170 --> 31:53.750
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

31:53.750 --> 31:54.250
No.

31:55.070 --> 31:55.530
It doesn't hurt.

31:56.990 --> 31:57.620
Doesn't hurt.

31:57.620 --> 32:01.130
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

32:01.410 --> 32:03.790
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

32:03.790 --> 32:07.900
I came to tell you

32:09.840 --> 32:11.450
that when I said I hated you,

32:12.640 --> 32:14.250
I was lying.

32:15.160 --> 32:16.100
Don't cry.

32:19.510 --> 32:21.250
I love you.

32:21.250 --> 32:25.490
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

32:26.160 --> 32:27.490
Until death.

32:27.490 --> 32:30.170
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

32:30.530 --> 32:33.370
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

32:34.360 --> 32:34.970
Miaoqing.

32:34.970 --> 32:40.200
♪Leaping straight into that heartbreaking past♪

32:42.710 --> 32:43.210
Miaoqing.

32:44.790 --> 32:45.420
Miaoqing!

32:46.310 --> 32:47.050
Miaoqing!

32:54.120 --> 32:56.050
Miaoqing, wake up!

32:57.120 --> 32:57.660
Miaoqing!

32:59.360 --> 33:00.530
Wake up!

33:04.470 --> 33:05.010
Miaoqing.

33:06.510 --> 33:07.250
Miaoqing!

33:18.640 --> 33:19.900
Miaoqing.

33:19.900 --> 33:21.970
♪My breath is about to stop♪

33:22.090 --> 33:25.610
♪Those hands can no longer hold yours♪

33:25.730 --> 33:29.170
♪Through the future snow, wind, and fog♪

33:29.330 --> 33:32.120
♪Who will be there by your side?♪

33:32.520 --> 33:35.920
♪I smile as it ends♪

33:36.320 --> 33:39.720
♪Afraid that you might cry for me♪

33:40.080 --> 33:41.510
♪Quietly, I turn into a sky lantern♪

33:41.510 --> 33:42.380
Let him go.

33:44.400 --> 33:45.140
He's probably

33:45.140 --> 33:46.710
♪To light your way through the night♪

33:46.710 --> 33:47.860
in more pain than death right now.

33:47.910 --> 33:48.820
♪Knowing love and hate♪

33:49.140 --> 33:53.060
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

33:54.420 --> 33:56.020
♪I still linger on♪

33:56.420 --> 34:00.620
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

34:01.020 --> 34:05.380
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

34:05.660 --> 34:08.620
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

34:08.940 --> 34:12.380
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

34:12.740 --> 34:15.860
♪I wish you well♪

34:16.180 --> 34:17.860
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

34:18.220 --> 34:22.140
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

34:23.500 --> 34:25.140
♪You're still screaming♪

34:25.420 --> 34:29.740
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

34:30.180 --> 34:34.420
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

34:34.780 --> 34:37.620
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

34:37.940 --> 34:40.100
♪I'd shatter my soul♪

34:40.500 --> 34:45.020
♪To lay all your days in peace♪

34:45.020 --> 34:47.060
♪Who says that love and hate♪

34:47.380 --> 34:52.180
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped?♪

34:52.420 --> 34:54.300
♪I will level the seas and mountains♪

34:54.620 --> 34:58.900
♪Break the waves, no matter how mad it seems♪

34:59.220 --> 35:03.580
♪The storm looms, yet I stand in its way♪

35:03.940 --> 35:06.820
♪Torn inside, still I burn bright♪

35:07.140 --> 35:13.220
♪With the light from my fingertips, I build a paradise♪

35:13.940 --> 35:17.500
♪To wander with you♪

35:39.070 --> 35:39.570
What are you doing?

35:39.800 --> 35:40.490
No take-backs.

35:40.720 --> 35:41.780
Know what "no take-backs" means?

35:41.880 --> 35:42.820
Do you even know how to play?

35:42.840 --> 35:43.780
Know what "no take-backs" means?

35:43.800 --> 35:44.340
Move your hand.

35:44.440 --> 35:45.130
I put it here,

35:45.150 --> 35:46.090
but I haven't let go yet.

35:46.110 --> 35:46.940
Does that count as a move?

35:47.320 --> 35:48.010
I'm still holding it.

35:48.030 --> 35:48.970
Does that count?

35:49.150 --> 35:49.740
It's called thinking.

35:49.760 --> 35:50.610
You just put it right there.

35:50.630 --> 35:51.650
It's called thinking. Understand?

35:52.030 --> 35:52.940
Do you know how to play?

35:53.030 --> 35:53.900
If you don't,

35:53.920 --> 35:55.010
let's just stop.

35:55.030 --> 35:55.940
Don't be a sore loser.

35:55.960 --> 35:56.300
Sore loser?

35:56.320 --> 35:57.570
You just put it there.

36:02.630 --> 36:03.610
Hey! Give that back!

36:04.190 --> 36:05.530
How dare you steal my wine?

36:06.240 --> 36:08.220
Why are you getting stingier with age?

36:08.670 --> 36:09.450
Stingy?

36:10.360 --> 36:12.570
This is the wine Lifei and Xiuyuan gave me.

36:12.880 --> 36:13.820
If you want wine, drink your own.

36:14.070 --> 36:15.260
Didn't they give you some too?

36:15.840 --> 36:17.490
I finished mine last night.

36:17.510 --> 36:18.820
What's that got to do with me?

36:19.030 --> 36:19.970
Just let me have one sip.

36:20.550 --> 36:21.820
Go away.

36:22.630 --> 36:23.780
Just one sip.

36:24.550 --> 36:25.300
Go away.

36:25.320 --> 36:25.860
Hey.

36:26.190 --> 36:28.700
Just one sip. One sip.

36:29.280 --> 36:29.900
What are you doing?

36:30.510 --> 36:31.700
Getting all worked up?

36:31.990 --> 36:32.700
I'm telling you,

36:32.920 --> 36:33.530
if you keep this up,

36:33.720 --> 36:35.130
I'll report you to Mr. Deng.

36:35.360 --> 36:36.300
I'll report you for being shameless,

36:36.510 --> 36:37.700
a drunkard,

36:37.720 --> 36:39.820
and disgracing Wuyue Court!

36:40.030 --> 36:41.170
You old geezer.

36:42.110 --> 36:42.530
I...

36:43.590 --> 36:45.570
You'll report me? I'll report you!

36:45.760 --> 36:47.260
For having bad chess etiquette!

36:47.280 --> 36:48.050
Alright.

36:48.070 --> 36:48.940
For going back on your word!

36:49.150 --> 36:49.740
Enough!

36:50.400 --> 36:51.340
Xiguang is busy.

36:51.630 --> 36:52.970
He doesn't have time for this.

36:53.320 --> 36:54.170
It's just wine.

36:54.550 --> 36:55.090
Have mine.

36:55.320 --> 36:56.650
This is from Lifei and Xiuyuan.

36:59.630 --> 37:00.610
That's more like it.

37:01.070 --> 37:01.900
Look at him.

37:03.760 --> 37:04.050
Here.

37:04.240 --> 37:05.450
Cheers.

37:05.470 --> 37:05.780
Here.

37:05.800 --> 37:06.450
Look at you two.

37:06.960 --> 37:08.130
Can you act like elders?

37:09.280 --> 37:09.940
Leave some for me.

37:36.110 --> 37:37.130
Fame and glory all over the capital.

37:37.130 --> 37:39.510
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

37:39.830 --> 37:41.110
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

37:41.110 --> 37:42.860
Just a dream in the end.

37:42.860 --> 37:46.110
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

37:46.350 --> 37:47.150
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

37:47.150 --> 37:48.380
All empty.

37:49.590 --> 37:53.070
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

37:53.790 --> 37:56.150
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

37:56.750 --> 37:58.270
♪No calamity can rival♪

37:58.670 --> 38:01.710
♪The lingering thread of a fragrance♪

38:03.850 --> 38:07.330
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

38:08.090 --> 38:10.330
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

38:10.770 --> 38:13.810
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge. Past the pagoda♪

38:14.450 --> 38:16.730
♪in fine robes on galloping horses♪

38:17.720 --> 38:18.380
Miaoqing.

38:18.380 --> 38:21.010
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

38:21.670 --> 38:23.950
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

38:24.470 --> 38:27.430
♪Betrayed by all, I still♪

38:28.150 --> 38:30.350
♪Reign supreme♪

38:31.130 --> 38:34.040
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

38:49.070 --> 38:49.820
Three-one-zero.

38:50.880 --> 38:51.900
- This is your exam number.
- Three-one-zero.

38:52.720 --> 38:53.450
Go line up over there.

38:53.590 --> 38:54.300
Three-one-zero.

38:56.510 --> 38:57.340
What's your name?

38:57.670 --> 38:58.490
Three-two-two.

38:59.150 --> 39:00.700
This is my clan nephew, Xing.

39:02.880 --> 39:04.740
You can tell he's a fine young monster.

39:06.030 --> 39:06.700
Come on.

39:06.990 --> 39:07.820
This is your exam number.

39:08.440 --> 39:08.820
Good luck!

39:10.280 --> 39:11.090
Three-two-nine.

39:11.590 --> 39:12.340
What's your name?

39:12.630 --> 39:13.170
Which clan?

39:13.190 --> 39:13.860
Three-two-nine.

39:17.670 --> 39:18.420
This is your exam number.

39:18.440 --> 39:18.700
Here.

39:18.960 --> 39:19.380
Okay.

39:19.670 --> 39:20.420
Go line up over there.

39:28.760 --> 39:30.610
Today is everyone's first day at the academy.

39:32.070 --> 39:34.050
First, you must know that the path of cultivation

39:34.630 --> 39:36.380
requires a dedicated heart.

39:37.880 --> 39:39.050
What is a dedicated heart?

39:41.670 --> 39:42.820
It could be for a personal wish

39:44.110 --> 39:45.450
or for the greater good.

39:46.440 --> 39:48.450
Turn to the first page.

40:05.110 --> 40:07.220
No wonder the Lord wanted to stay in the Central Plains.

40:07.590 --> 40:09.610
The people and the food here are wonderful.

40:10.070 --> 40:11.860
You folks from across the sea are wonderful too.

40:11.880 --> 40:12.700
So carefree.

40:13.240 --> 40:14.170
What's it like across the sea?

40:14.510 --> 40:15.700
We have thousands of islands.

40:16.070 --> 40:17.260
Each one is different.

40:17.590 --> 40:19.010
There are mermaids in the sea

40:19.360 --> 40:20.820
and winged unicorns.

40:21.550 --> 40:22.740
There are winged unicorns?

40:22.760 --> 40:23.300
Of course.

40:23.990 --> 40:25.010
They must be able to fly.

40:25.150 --> 40:25.700
Don't believe me?

40:26.150 --> 40:27.490
I'll take you to see them someday.

40:28.070 --> 40:28.700
Good!

40:29.070 --> 40:30.420
I wonder how Lifei is doing.

40:34.190 --> 40:35.340
Probably like us.

40:36.440 --> 40:37.260
Wherever she goes, he follows.

40:56.800 --> 41:00.240
[The Demon Lord's Beloved Wife. The Immortal Lord's Undying Love]

41:06.760 --> 41:07.820
Turn in your manuscript now.

41:07.990 --> 41:09.530
The Central Plains and those across the sea love your work.

41:09.840 --> 41:11.130
Especially the Chufeng Trilogy.

41:11.360 --> 41:13.700
It's sparked a wave of new applicants to the academy.

41:14.150 --> 41:15.300
You must turn in the next chapters

41:15.320 --> 41:16.490
by Chen hour tomorrow.

41:16.880 --> 41:17.300
Or else...

41:17.880 --> 41:18.570
Always rushing!

41:18.800 --> 41:19.610
Annoying book merchants.

41:21.550 --> 41:23.220
Lifei, food's ready!

41:31.720 --> 41:34.450
Dear, your cooking keeps getting better.

41:35.110 --> 41:35.650
Here.

41:37.360 --> 41:38.340
Have a piece of meat.

41:51.670 --> 41:52.820
Dear, your storybooks are a hit.

41:53.470 --> 41:56.050
The bookshop's profits just got us another ten mu of land.

41:56.510 --> 41:56.940
Here.

42:00.150 --> 42:01.450
Have some radish.

42:04.590 --> 42:05.010
Delicious.

42:05.720 --> 42:06.170
Delicious.

42:13.320 --> 42:14.220
Have some greens.

42:15.630 --> 42:16.170
Here.

42:18.840 --> 42:20.700
Are you two treating me like air?

42:24.760 --> 42:25.170
Alright.

42:25.470 --> 42:26.260
Then let's feed him together.

42:26.320 --> 42:26.740
You, eat.

42:27.150 --> 42:27.740
Come on.

42:28.440 --> 42:28.900
Here.

42:29.360 --> 42:30.130
Try some.

42:30.920 --> 42:32.260
- Stop running! - Just one bite.

42:32.590 --> 42:34.220
One bite and you'll know. It's amazing.

42:34.550 --> 42:35.900
Try some radish.

42:35.920 --> 42:36.820
Why are you running so fast?

42:36.920 --> 42:38.300
I grew it myself!

42:38.840 --> 42:39.610
Stop him, Lifei!

42:39.630 --> 42:40.900
Amazing radish!

42:42.050 --> 42:42.780
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:42.780 --> 42:44.560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:55.800 --> 42:59.480
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

42:59.800 --> 43:02.480
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

43:02.560 --> 43:05.800
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

43:05.800 --> 43:09.080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

43:09.200 --> 43:13.080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

43:13.360 --> 43:16.560
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

43:16.720 --> 43:22.800
♪No calamity can rival the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

43:23.080 --> 43:27.200
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

43:27.480 --> 43:30.160
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

43:30.360 --> 43:32.280
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

43:32.400 --> 43:36.720
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

43:36.880 --> 43:40.720
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

43:41.080 --> 43:44.080
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

43:44.160 --> 43:50.280
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

43:50.480 --> 43:54.200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

44:07.440 --> 44:11.200
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

44:11.400 --> 44:14.200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

44:14.280 --> 44:17.680
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

44:17.680 --> 44:21.000
♪Yet I remain silent♪

44:21.160 --> 44:25.000
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

44:25.160 --> 44:28.360
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

44:28.600 --> 44:34.440
♪The grand chapter is rewritten, startling the whole world♪

44:35.000 --> 44:38.920
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

44:39.200 --> 44:41.960
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

44:42.160 --> 44:44.000
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

44:44.160 --> 44:48.360
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

44:48.600 --> 44:52.480
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

44:52.720 --> 44:55.760
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

44:55.960 --> 45:02.680
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

45:02.720 --> 45:06.680
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

45:06.920 --> 45:09.680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

45:09.800 --> 45:11.720
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

45:11.880 --> 45:16.160
♪Break through the waves; the heart's ocean knows no shore♪

45:16.360 --> 45:20.200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

45:20.440 --> 45:23.560
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

45:23.600 --> 45:29.600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water and falling petals♪

45:30.000 --> 45:34.360
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪
